0:00:00.300,0:00:01.060
Ema ka dinao.

0:00:01.060,0:00:03.460
A re rapele thapelo e.

0:00:03.460,0:00:19.060
Kopa Modimo gogo neela mohau go se lebale tumelo ya gago le fa ole kafatlase ga kgatlelelo ya meleko

0:00:19.060,0:00:21.300
ya makowa le malwetse

0:00:21.300,0:00:22.520
Kopa Modimo gogo fa mohau.

0:00:22.520,0:00:26.640
Mphe mohau, Morena, ke se lebale tumelo yame

0:00:26.640,0:00:41.760
ka fa tlase ga kgatlelelo kana boima jwa meleko ya bokowa, bolwetse, mathata le poelo morago.

0:00:58.300,0:01:04.340
Sengwe le sengwe se o se raletseng ka fa tlase ga meleko eo, kopa Modimo, Morena Jeso,

0:01:04.340,0:01:13.580
neela mohau ke seka ka ikgatholosa tumelo yame kele kafa tlase ga meloko ya diemo tsame.

0:01:13.580,0:01:15.940
Seemo sa gago ke eng?

0:01:15.940,0:01:22.100
Fa seemo se goroga, re tlelwa kego lebala gore re bakeresete.

0:01:48.280,0:01:50.320
Ka leina la Jeso Keresete.

0:01:50.320,0:01:51.200
[Amene]

0:01:51.200,0:02:08.820
O a lebala, fao raletse kgwetlho, kana seemo, gore o sone se Modimo areng o sone;

0:02:08.820,0:02:13.040
o kgona go dira se Modimo areng o ka se dira

0:02:13.040,0:02:18.480
O lebego o lebala gore o nale se Modimo areng o nale sone.

0:02:18.480,0:02:23.400
Modimo a nale wena, sengwe le sengwe sa kgonega

0:02:23.400,0:02:29.480
Go lebega o lebala seo fa o raletse dikgwetho.

0:02:32.420,0:02:35.440
Wena le Modimo ga mmogo

0:02:35.440,0:02:43.260
Go lebega o lebala gore wena le Modimo le ka sutisa dithaba fao raletse dikgwetho.

0:02:43.260,0:02:45.720
Le tshwanetse la kopana; wena le mang?

0:02:45.720,0:02:47.360
[Modimo.]

0:02:47.360,0:02:51.660
Wena le Modimo le tshwanetse la kopana, la tshwaragana ka diatla gammogo.

0:02:51.660,0:02:57.780
Ga gona thaba, ebile ga go ketla gonna le thaba.

0:02:57.780,0:03:04.900
Wena le Modimo - mme go lebega o lebala se fa o raletse eng?

0:03:04.900,0:03:06.680
Bothata.

0:03:06.680,0:03:16.800
O tshwanetse wa gakologelwa mathata le diemo tsa nako tseo fetileng mogo tsone bogologolo.

0:03:16.800,0:03:25.260
Selotlelo sa go atlega mo botshelong hao le ngwana wa Modimo ke - nako nngwe le nngwe fao raletse mathata

0:03:25.260,0:03:33.720
ka pela o gakologelwe mathata le diemo tseo di raletseng mo nako ee fetileng.

0:03:33.720,0:03:43.080
Sena se tla go tlisetsa matla a go ka fenya mathata ao leng mogo one.

0:03:48.440,0:03:50.680
Tsaya nako ya gago goka gakologelwa.

0:03:50.680,0:03:54.700
Sena ke se se diragaletseng Tafite.

0:03:54.700,0:03:59.500
Tafite o ile fa pele ga ga kgosi ka borena mme are,

0:03:59.500,0:04:06.640
'Kgosi, Ke tsile go lebagana le Golite yoo tshwentseng barwa rre le lefatshe lame'.

0:04:06.640,0:04:09.440
Kgosi a mo leba: 'O mang wena?'

0:04:09.440,0:04:16.920
Are, 'Ke dirisitse diatla tsame go bolaya bera'.

0:04:16.920,0:04:30.640
Fa monna yo atla go tshwenya lefatshe la bone, ka bofefo a gakologelwa diemo tse di thata tse a di fentseng.

0:04:30.640,0:04:38.780
Go gakologelweng bera, a leba Golite mme are, "ta ke lebagane le monna yo"

0:04:38.780,0:04:45.340
Ka mokgwa oo, ke yone tsela ya go fenya seemo sa gago sa nako eo.

0:04:45.340,0:04:51.620
Bolelela mabapi wa gago, "Se ke sone selotlelo sa go fenya seemo same sa nako eno".

0:04:51.620,0:04:56.440
O ka dirisa selotlelo seo goka lotlolola kgotsa go lotlela.

0:04:56.440,0:05:03.260
Gakologelwa fela jaaka Tafite a gakologetswe, mme atsamaya ko go Kgosi ka borena.

0:05:03.260,0:05:07.680
Tsaya nako ya gago.

0:05:07.680,0:05:18.460
Nako nngwe le nngwe fao raletse kgwetho kgotsa seemo, gakologelwa mathata o fetileng ka one

0:05:18.460,0:05:24.240
mo nako ee fetileng mme waa fenya.

0:05:24.240,0:05:34.700
Seo se tla go tlatsa ka matla ago fenya seemo sa nako eo.

0:05:34.700,0:05:42.220
Ga ke itse sepe seke ka se ralalang gompieno ebile se fetla se ke setseng kese raletse.

0:05:42.220,0:05:43.080
A wa bona?

0:05:43.080,0:05:46.400
Ka jalo, ga ke itse seo ka se ralalang jaana

0:05:46.400,0:05:49.900
se se fetang seo setseng o kila wa feta ka sone.

0:05:49.900,0:05:57.140
Fa o ka gakologelwa se, se ka go tsenya matla go ka lebagana le seemo  sa nako e.

0:05:57.140,0:06:05.340
Wa gakologelwa - sephatlo sa rona ba releng hana retswa magaeng, ebile gongwe 90% ya batho mo.

0:06:05.340,0:06:10.840
O tshwanetse wa gakologelwa nako tseo neng o nwa metsi aa leswe.

0:06:10.840,0:06:19.400
Mme tsatsi jeno le nwa metsi a phepha, le mororo -  letshoroma.

0:06:22.100,0:06:26.140
Lenwa metsi aa phepha.

0:06:26.140,0:06:30.200
Letshoroma le tswa kae?

0:06:30.200,0:06:33.340
Mpolelele.

0:06:33.340,0:06:36.920
Wena, o tswa legaeng.

0:06:36.920,0:06:46.060
Gakologelwa - mo nakong tsele, fao apaya supo, one o nna oe thathafatsa ga malatsi ale lesome.

0:06:46.060,0:06:50.720
Ebile ha onna oe thuthafatsa e nnela monate ko pele.

0:06:57.280,0:07:00.140
A o ka thuthafatsa supo malatsia?

0:07:00.140,0:07:03.660
Fa o apaya supo tsatsi jeno, a oka e thuthafatsa kamoso wa eja?

0:07:03.660,0:07:04.920
[Nnyaa]

0:07:04.920,0:07:07.380
Mme ko legaeng...

0:07:07.380,0:07:12.340
Tse ke tsone dilo tse di go godisitseng.

0:07:12.340,0:07:15.160
Gakologelwa kaha o tshotsweng ka teng.

0:07:15.160,0:07:21.380
Bontsi jwa lona ga loa tsholelwa mo dikokelong.

0:07:21.380,0:07:27.840
Batho bao ba bitsang baba gompieno, ke bone baba neng bago jesa fa one ole ngwana.

0:07:27.840,0:07:36.900
Mmago ale nosi nko asa kgona gogo thokomela - one o togelwa o tsamaya fa gare ga bone,

0:07:36.900,0:07:43.480
mme tsatsi jeno o ba bona ele batho baba ka go bolayang.

0:07:43.480,0:07:46.840
Se ke sone selotlelo seke se lo nayang  tsatsi jeno.

0:07:46.840,0:07:58.640
Nako nngwe le nngwe fao lebagane le seemo, gakologelwa mathata le diemo tseo fetileng mogo tsone.

0:07:58.640,0:08:00.860
Se se tla go tsenya eng?

0:08:00.860,0:08:02.760
[Matla]

0:08:02.760,0:08:05.120
Go dira eng?

0:08:05.120,0:08:07.020
Go lebagana leng?

0:08:07.020,0:08:09.440
Go lebagana le seemo seo mo go some.

0:08:09.440,0:08:11.820
O thokana le matla.

0:08:17.320,0:08:19.740
A o bua ka tiro ya gago?

0:08:19.740,0:08:23.680
Gakologelwa sekolo seo tseneng mogo sone ko magaeng.

0:08:23.680,0:08:26.160
Sekolo sese senang marulelo.

0:08:26.160,0:08:27.420
Sekolo sese seng eng?

0:08:27.420,0:08:29.080
[Marulelo.]

0:08:29.080,0:08:38.120
O ithutetse ka hatlase ga dipula, letsatsi - mme leba gore tsatsi jeno o nnile eng.

0:08:38.120,0:08:43.980
Fa o sa itse mofutla wa sekolo seo tseneng mogo sone nako tsele ko legaeng - boele ko legaeng

0:08:43.980,0:08:49.500
o ye go bona fa bana ba ithutelang teng.

0:08:49.500,0:08:52.140
Tse ke tsone dilo tseo di lomaganyang.

0:08:52.140,0:08:56.640
Fa o akanya ka tsone dilo tse, o ta lemoga fa go sena yoo ka go thibelang.

0:08:56.640,0:09:03.240
o re, "Kenna hela yo ke ka ithibelang; e seng ope gape."

0:09:03.240,0:09:07.440
Ga gona yo oka go thibelang; go ka ithibela wena hela.

0:09:07.440,0:09:14.420
Fa ele gore ga gone sese go thibetseng ka nako ele, gompieno, ga gona yoo ka go thibelang.

0:09:19.660,0:09:25.920
O thokana le matla goya pele.

0:09:25.920,0:09:30.740
Ke gone ka ha nna ke ikgodisang ka teng.

0:09:30.740,0:09:42.100
Go sa kgathalesege sese tlang kogo nna, ke nna haatshe ke bo ke gakologelwa ditiragalo tsa ko ke tswang teng,

0:09:42.100,0:09:44.340
se ke hitileng mogo sone.

0:09:44.340,0:09:51.960
Se se diragalang jaana ke leba hela kebo kere "O ngwana".

0:09:55.520,0:09:57.600
Ke a nyenya.

0:09:57.600,0:10:07.740
Fa o sa fetole lethabo la gago ka seemo sa gago, wa fenya.

0:10:07.740,0:10:14.020
Bolelela mabapi, "Emisa go latlhegelwa ke lethabo la gago ka lebaka la seemo sa gago"

0:10:14.020,0:10:19.440
Fela fa oka emisa go latlha lethabo la gago ka lebaka la seemo seo leng mogo sone, o tla nna kago fenya

0:10:19.440,0:10:24.480
ka gore o thokana le lethabo go fenya seemo.

0:10:24.480,0:10:30.700
Go sa kgatlhalesege gore seemo sa gago se setona jang, fa o sa latlhegelwe ke lethabo la gago ka lebaka la seemo sa gago, o tla se henya.

0:10:30.700,0:10:34.740
Mme fa lethabo le gago le seo, ga o kake wa kgona go fenya seemo sa gago.

0:10:34.740,0:10:37.540
Se ke sone se seemo se batlang go se tsaya mogo wena.

0:10:37.540,0:10:39.940
Se leka go tsaya lethabo la gago.

0:10:39.940,0:10:41.200
Modimo wame.

0:10:41.200,0:10:44.100
Se batla gogo bona o hutsahetse

0:10:44.100,0:10:45.900
Seemo se batla gogo bona o rileng?

0:10:45.900,0:10:46.600
[O Hutsahetse]

0:10:46.600,0:10:49.940
Se bata gogo bona o hutsahetse.

0:10:49.940,0:10:53.280
Fela fa seemo se goroga oa hutsahala...

0:10:53.280,0:10:55.300
Ke tla dira jang?

0:10:55.300,0:10:56.760
Ao Modimo wame.

0:10:56.760,0:10:59.060
Se se bokete mogo nna.

0:10:59.060,0:11:02.320
Ka fa tlase ga seemo seo, ga o kgone go rapela.

0:11:02.320,0:11:05.500
Ka fa tlase ga seemo seo, ga o kgone go akanya Modimo.

0:11:05.500,0:11:11.220
Ka fa tlase ga seemo seo...

0:11:11.220,0:11:21.200
O tla latlhegelwa ke go akanya sentle, o bona mongwe le mongwe mogo wena ele mmaba wa gago.

0:11:21.200,0:11:24.440
O tla palelwa ke go ntsha bojotlhe jwa gago.

0:11:24.440,0:11:33.360
Ke araba mogalo: - Dumelang - Ntlo ya gago e kapile molelo

0:11:33.360,0:11:39.440
- O raya ntlo yame? - Ee. Go thwahetse. Ba tima molelo ba koo.

0:11:39.440,0:11:42.600
Pele ga moo kene ke nyenya.

0:11:49.700,0:11:53.480
Batho ba ke nag le bone ba go botsa, "Go diragetse eng jaanong?"

0:11:53.480,0:11:54.780
Ke etla.

0:11:54.780,0:11:58.540
Ke fetlotse eng same?

0:11:58.540,0:11:59.940
[Lethabo]

0:11:59.940,0:12:00.660
Ka eng?

0:12:00.660,0:12:02.200
[Seemo]

0:12:06.760,0:12:09.300
Itebelele - o tumetse jaanong.

0:12:09.300,0:12:13.320
Saatane wa itse gore o ka dira eng goka emisa lethabo leo.

0:12:13.320,0:12:15.700
Wa itse.

0:12:15.700,0:12:20.280
Mongwe o bata gogo bona mme o santse o bina

0:12:20.280,0:12:22.080
Kae?

0:12:22.080,0:12:23.400
Go mpona.

0:12:25.400,0:12:26.700
Kae?

0:12:29.620,0:12:34.040
O seka wa e dira gore go nne mothofo mogo saatane.

0:12:34.040,0:12:36.500
Mongwe wa go lwantsha.

0:12:36.500,0:12:43.040
Wa iketla go nale go thabana - o go dira gore go senne le boleng.

0:12:43.040,0:12:47.560
Mongwe o bata gogo bona mme o santse o bina.

0:12:47.580,0:12:50.700
Kae?

0:12:50.700,0:12:53.200
Ehe gone koo. Ke etla.

0:12:53.200,0:12:56.440
O bata go feleletsa go bina ga gago.

0:12:56.440,0:12:58.820
Ke bale kae mogo lona ba lo ka dirang jalo?

0:12:58.820,0:13:03.680
A lokile lwa hetsa go bina pele ga lo ya go bona mongwe yo neng a batla gole bona?

0:13:03.680,0:13:06.880
nnyaa kea lo itse.

0:13:06.880,0:13:14.360
Ka tswee tswee, emisa go fetola lethabo la gago mo seemong.

0:13:14.360,0:13:24.180
Fa o nale bothoko mo letsogong, oka thopha gosa emisetsa lethabo la gago ka seemo.

0:13:24.180,0:13:25.440
O tsogile jang?

0:13:25.440,0:13:26.540
Ke siame.

0:13:26.540,0:13:28.340
Bothoko bo santse bole teng.

0:13:28.340,0:13:29.780
Ke siame

0:13:29.780,0:13:32.080
Ke ntse kesa go bone.

0:13:32.080,0:13:33.520
Ke ntse kele teng.

0:13:33.520,0:13:35.240
ee.

0:13:35.240,0:13:37.340
Bothoko bontse bo mogo nna.

0:13:37.340,0:13:41.040
Bothoko joo ga bo batle go utlwa lethabo.

0:13:41.040,0:13:54.620
Fa gonang le boitumelo le bothoko teng, bothoko joo ga bo ketla bo diega.

0:13:54.620,0:14:01.760
Fa go nang le kutlobothoko le lethabo dile ga mmogo, lethabo leo ga le ketla le diega.

0:14:01.760,0:14:04.220
Ga di tsamaisane.

0:14:04.220,0:14:07.680
Okare katse le peba.

0:14:07.680,0:14:14.700
Fa o thopha go nna o itumetse ontse o batla tiro, o tla e bona.

0:14:18.100,0:14:29.980
Fa o lwala, mme wa ikgethela gonna o itumetse mo pelong - bolwetse joo ga bo ketla bo nna.

0:14:29.980,0:14:36.480
Fa lenyalo la gago lele mo kotsing, mongwe a leka gole thakathakanya -

0:14:36.480,0:14:40.480
thopha go itumela, o tle o bone gore go tla diragala eng.

0:14:40.480,0:14:47.020
A wa itse gore ke seemo sese latelang lethabo; gase lethabo lele lateng seemo.

0:14:47.020,0:14:54.740
Bolelelamabapi wa gago, "Seemo se latlela lethabo; lethabo ga le latele seemo."

0:14:54.740,0:14:59.420
Fa o ka ithuta botshelo jwa gago seemo ke sone se lateng lethabo.

0:14:59.420,0:15:04.840
Mo botshelong jwa motho, seemo se latlela lethabo.

0:15:04.840,0:15:10.760
Lethabo ke lone le go laolang, seemo gase go laole.

0:15:10.760,0:15:12.980
seemo se latela lethabo.

0:15:12.980,0:15:15.720
Fa noga etla ko ntlong ya gago o tswala lebati.

0:15:15.720,0:15:20.600
Ga o sie o bulela noga e tsena fa kgorong.

0:15:20.600,0:15:24.220
Emisa go fetola lethabo la gago ka eng?

0:15:24.220,0:15:25.880
[Seemo sa gago.]

0:15:25.880,0:15:39.140
Fa oka dira se, diemo di tlaatla mme ga di ketla di diega mme ka jalo o tla uthuta sengwe sese tla go thusang.

0:15:44.300,0:15:48.260
Lebelela di emo tse ke di raletseng ko tshimologong.

0:15:48.260,0:15:52.340
Leina la kereke e lene le sa tshwanela go bitswa gotwe "Kereke ya ditshaba tshaba".

0:15:52.340,0:16:00.400
Fane kere ene e nale maloko ale lesome le boroba bobedi (8), Morena o ne are ke "Kereke ya ditshabatshaba".

0:16:02.620,0:16:10.340
Ke dile kahe dikereke ko mafatsheng a lona tse eleng  "ya ditshaba tshaba"?

0:16:13.780,0:16:19.740
Fa ne ise kereke ya ponelopele le maikemisetso...

0:16:19.740,0:16:22.280
Kereke ya ntlha ya senyega, ya bobedi ya senyega.

0:16:22.280,0:16:27.600
Ke bale kae baba leng mo dikgwebong tse ba simolotseng ka tsone?

0:16:27.600,0:16:33.540
Ga ke dumele gore ope wa lona o santse ale mo kgwebong, yaa simolotseng ka yone pele.

0:16:33.540,0:16:35.960
Morago ga dikgwetho tse dintsi...

0:16:35.960,0:16:40.040
Fao sa itse koo go yang gao kitla o tswelela.

0:16:40.040,0:16:44.620
O ka se kgone go emela kgololo ya Modimo fao sa itse koo go yang.

0:16:44.620,0:16:48.600
Ke hao itse koo go yang ke gone o tla emelang kgololo ya Modimo.

0:16:48.600,0:16:55.080
Bua le mabapi, "Fa o itse koo go yang o tla emela kgololo ya Modimo;

0:16:55.080,0:16:58.560
O tla ema ka bopelotlelele go gololwa ke Modimo."

0:16:58.560,0:17:08.180
Mme fa o sa itse koo ogo yaang o a ikgolola.

0:17:11.240,0:17:13.720
Ontse o ikgolola.

0:17:13.720,0:17:21.240
O ikgolola mo kgwebong, mo lenyalong, mo kerekeng, gongwe le gongwe wa...

0:17:21.240,0:17:22.700
Matlhabisa dithong...

0:17:22.700,0:17:24.440
O ka bua maaka kanna jaana?

0:17:24.440,0:17:25.680
Wa tsamaya.

0:17:25.680,0:17:32.560
O tlogela setshaba, kgwebo, kereke kana lenyalo.

0:17:32.560,0:17:34.220
Ke matlhapa a mohutla mang a?

0:17:34.220,0:17:37.120
Se ke mathabisa ditlhong, ga ke dumele seo se buang.

0:17:37.120,0:17:40.720
Moruti yo ke eng a bua maaka ka nna?

0:17:40.720,0:17:44.840
O tswa mo kerekeng

0:17:44.840,0:17:49.320
Mo lenyalong gape - monna wame o bua maaka ka nna.

0:17:49.320,0:17:51.260
Mosadi wame oka ntira jaana.

0:17:51.260,0:17:54.600
Otswa mo lenyalong

0:17:54.600,0:17:56.780
Kgwebo - Modimo wame.

0:17:56.780,0:17:58.480
Ke tshwanetse go tlhatlosiwa maemo.

0:17:58.480,0:18:01.160
Lebelela yoo hatlase game - ke rutile monna yo tiro.

0:18:01.160,0:18:04.220
Mmone - o tlhatlositswe maemo godimo game.

0:18:04.220,0:18:07.400
O tlogela kgwebo.

0:18:07.400,0:18:09.640
Jo ke jone botshelo jo lentseng le bo tshela.

0:18:09.640,0:18:11.560
Diemo dintse digo tlogela.

0:18:11.560,0:18:13.800
Dikgwetho dintse di go tlogela.

0:18:13.800,0:18:17.520
O utwlile se Josefa ase buileng ha ane ale mo mosimeng.

0:18:17.520,0:18:20.600
O ne are, "Ke itse ko ke tshwanetseng gobo kele teng".

0:18:20.600,0:18:22.720
Ga o itse koo yang teng.

0:18:22.720,0:18:28.660
O ne ale mo mosimeng, ko neng go sena metsi, go sena phefo.

0:18:28.660,0:18:34.940
